            <span style="color:#337ab7;cursor:pointer" onclick="openCommunity()" >Community</span>
        </h3>
            <p>
                Join Octoparse Community to ask for help<br /> or share everything you know about web scraping!
            </p>
        <h3>
            <span style="color:#337ab7;cursor:pointer" onclick="open7()">Tutorials 7.X</span> |
            <span style="color:#337ab7;cursor:pointer" onclick="open6()">6.X</span>
        </h3>
        <p>Articles and guides to get you started<br>on your own scraping projects</p>
    </a>
</div>
